            <div class="col-md-6 text-justify">
                <h1 class="text-primary-narrative" id="text-title">Records of the House of Refuge</h1>
                <p id="text-primary-narrative" class="lead text-left">What remains of the records of the House of Refuge are now housed at the
                    University of Cincinnati's
                    <%= link_to 'Archives and Rare Books Library. ', 'http://www.libraries.uc.edu/arb.html', target: '_blank' %>The records were transferred to the University of Cincinnati from the
